ZITADEL achieves ISO 27001 certification, reinforcing commitment to security



[http://0wkkr.mjt.lu/img2/0wkkr/6c879f4f-bef0-4282-89a2-b0c6aa1e3b62/content]

In a significant milestone for ZITADEL's commitment to security and data protection, we have achieved ISO 27001 certification for our information security management system (ISMS). This internationally recognized standard validates our dedication to maintaining the highest levels of security for our customers' data. 

To provide further transparency and information about our security practices, we have also updated our Trust Center [https://trust.zitadel.com]. This resource offers comprehensive details on our security posture, policies, and certifications.



<<Blog: ZITADEL Achieves ISO 27001 Certification>> [https://zitadel.com/blog/zitadel-iso-27001-certified]




